  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Clear
    This command is responsible for clearing the screen when prompted.
    Continue
    This command is responsible for continuing a dialog when prompted.
    Go
    This command is responsible for moving through rooms and locations.
    Help
    This command is responsible for helping the player with information.
    Inspect
    This command is responsible for inspecting a room when prompted.
    Interact
    This command is responsible for interacting with GameObject's in the current room.
    Quit
    This command is responsible for quitting the game when prompted.
    Show
    This command is responsible for showing resources to the player.
    Start
    This command is responsible for starting the Wave.
